This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and generation using recurrent neural network models. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it involves the development of an AI chatbot. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it uses machine learning techniques to train the models. The paper also involves human-computer interaction, which could place it under cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction). Finally, it could be categorized under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as it involves the evaluation of the chatbot's responses using human evaluators.
